{
  "texts": [
    "The authors simulated a classroom scenario using CGMI.Jurisprudence: LLM-based agents can serve as aids in legal decision-making processes, facilitating more informed judgements [112,113].",
    "Blind Judgement [113] employs several language models to simulate the decision-making processes of multiple judges.",
    "It gathers diverse opinions and consolidates the outcomes through a voting mechanism.",
    "ChatLaw [112] is a prominent Chinese legal model based on LLM.",
    "It adeptly supports both database and keyword search strategies, specifically designed to mitigate the hallucination issue prevalent in such models."
  ]
}